{"word":"G2255 - ἥμισυ - hḗmisy - hay'-mee-soo - Half","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἥμισυ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hḗmisy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hay'-mee-soo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Half</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பாதி, அரை - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"half"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a derivative from an inseparable prefix akin to <a href=\"#/G260 - ἅμα - háma - ham'-ah/260\">G260</a> (through the idea of <i>partition</i> involved in <i>connection</i>) and meaning <i>semi-</i>; (as noun) <i>half:</i> - half.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}